stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> NEW: ApplicationMaster requests resource
    NEW --> ALLOCATED: Scheduler assigns resource & generates token
    ALLOCATED --> ACQUIRED: AM receives token in heartbeat response
    ACQUIRED --> STARTING: AM calls NM StartContainers() & localization begins
    STARTING --> RUNNING: Local resources ready, process launched under CGroups
    RUNNING --> COMPLETED: Task completes successfully (exit code 0)
    RUNNING --> FAILED: Task crashes / OOMs / fails (exit code != 0)
    RUNNING --> KILLED: AM / RM cancels container task
    COMPLETED --> [*]
    FAILED --> [*]
    KILLED --> [*]
